</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="D3AAF8FFFFA1FFC074B9FD61F849FD58" box="[255,268,741,767]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,255,1850,1874]" captionTargetBox="[162,1422,205,1811]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[155,1432,197,1823]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Males of Ponerinae. a – e, Odontomachus coquereli (CASENT 0049797). f, Leptogenys sp. (CASENT 0114506). (a) head to abdomen in lateral view; (b) petiole in anterior view; (c) head to abdomen in dorsal view; (d) head in full-face view; (e, f) apical portion of the abdomen in dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/274011/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="34">8</figureCitation>
a–e)
</paragraph>
